Package org.apache.jena.riot.system

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ErrorHandler
    An Error handler captures the policy for dealing with warnings, errors and fatal errors.
    ParserProfile  
    PrefixMap
    Interface for lightweight prefix maps, this is similar to PrefixMapping from Jena Core but it omits any reverse lookup functionality.
    StreamRDF
    The interface for the output of RDF, such as the RIOT parsers.

    Class Description
    Checker
    A checker validates RDF terms.
    ErrorHandlerFactory

    A prefix map implementation suited to output heavy workloads
    IRIResolver
    Package up IRI reolver functionality.
    JenaWriterBase  
    JenaWriterNTriples2  
    JenaWriterRdfJson  
    LangTag
    Language tags: support for parsing and canonicalization of case.
    MapWithScope<A,B,S>
    Maps A's to B's, based on a scope S
    ParserProfileBase
    Basic profile of things, with key operations based on a simple use of the parse elements into Nodes
    ParserProfileChecker  
    PrefixMapBase
    Abstract base implementation of a PrefixMap which provides some useful helper methods
    PrefixMapExtended
    Implementation of a PrefixMap which extends another prefix map without ever altering the parent.
    PrefixMapFactory
    Factory which provides prefix maps
    PrefixMapStd
    Default implementation of a PrefixMap, this implementation is best suited to use for input.
    Prologue  
    RiotChars  
    RiotLib

    SyntaxLabels
